(18822, 'Farcosef 500mg vial', 'فاركوسيف 500مجم فيال', '', '7', 'Cephradine', 'Pharco b', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antibiotic.cephalosporin.first-generation', '500mg', 'description a semi-synthetic cephalosporin antibiotic. mechanism of action cefradine is a first generation cephalosporin antibiotic with a spectrum of activity similar to cefalexin. cefradine like the penicillins is a beta-lactam antibiotic. by binding to', '6223000010884', '', 753, '2023-02-06', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
